sentences: Steve Rifkind's SRC/Universal recognized his strong work ethic, and more importantly his talent, and signed Massey to a recording deal in 2005.
Massey now splits time between Chicago and Atlanta, the latter being home base to Stephens’ management company UpFront Megatainment.
In 2011, Massey released the album Love D.N.A. In talking about the album, he said, "My definition for Love D.N. A is baby-making music.
"You can go from looking up to a lady's man, or …  you can look up to a pastor.
